   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_2_00020"/><hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb40788" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Villa</hi> Platzer</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb34824" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Seeboden</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb39637" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">am Millstätter</hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_2_00021"/><salute>lieber;</salute> es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>olut un<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>innnig, am 1. Tag<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o ra<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>end zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>trapaziren, und be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>onders we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> der 2. Tag die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chwierig<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Partie (<rs ref="#pmb43070" type="place">Giau</rs>) enthält und <del rend="strikethrough">die</del> wir doch nur möglich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t arbeitsfri<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch betreten
               wollen. Wir werden daher die Tour I in 2 Tage zerlegen, dafür am 1. Tag den <rs ref="#pmb43067" type="place">Prag<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er See</rs> mitnehmen. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> bleibt es auch gewahrt d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s alle Nachmittag frei<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind. – Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibe Ihnen das gleich hier, um nicht nervös zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein. –</p><closer>Herzliche Grüße Ihr <signed>A. S.</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><rs ref="#pmb41052" type="place">Spital</rs>, <date>31. 7. 99</date>, eben<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlägt’s <time>7 Uhr früh</time>.</dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
